Package: KSIC
Title: Korea Standard Industry Code (KSIC) Data
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Jongjin", "Yun", , "jongjin@uos.ac.kr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package offers a comprehensive toolkit for working with
    the Korea Standard Industrial Classification (KSIC). It includes complete
    datasets for the 9th, 10th, and 11th revisions of the KSIC. Key features
    include functions to search codes and names by keyword, convert codes
    across different revisions, validate KSIC codes, and navigate the classification
    hierarchy by identifying parent or child categories. The package is designed to
    support statistical analysis, data processing, and research related to
    South Korea's industrial classification standards.
